cat << EOF
GtkSpell provides MSWord/MacOSX-style highlighting of misspelled words in a GtkTextView 
widget as you type. Right-clicking a misspelled word pops up a menu of suggested replacements.

Note: this is a library for developers working with pspell, placed here to be near pspell.
EOF
